==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Insensibly
<hw>In*sen"si*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a manner not to be felt
or perceived; imperceptibly; gradually.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The hills rise <qex>insensibly</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insensitive</ent>⟦br⟧
